<section class="py-28 px-8 bg-surface-container-low" id="contact">
	<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
		<div class="mb-16">
			<span class="text-xs tracking-[0.2em] uppercase text-on-primary-container mb-4 block" style="font-family: var(--font-label)">Contact</span>
			<h2 class="text-4xl text-primary" style="font-family: var(--font-headline)">お問い合わせ</h2>
		</div>
		<div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16">
			<div>
				<p class="text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed mb-10 text-lg">
					プロジェクトのご相談、技術的な議論、あるいは単純に連絡を取りたい場合はお気軽にどうぞ。セキュリティ設計、法×ITの課題、大歓迎です。
				</p>
				<div class="space-y-6">
					<div class="flex items-center gap-4">
						<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-secondary">mail</span>
						<span class="text-on-surface-variant text-sm">フォームからメッセージをお送りください</span>
					</div>
					<div class="flex items-center gap-4">
						<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-secondary">schedule</span>
						<span class="text-on-surface-variant text-sm">通常 2 営業日以内にご返信します</span>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
			<form class="space-y-6" action="https://formspree.io/f/meepjvry" method="POST" novalidate>
				<div>
					<label class="block text-xs tracking-widest uppercase text-on-surface-variant mb-2" for="name" style="font-family: var(--font-label)">お名前</label>
					<input
						class="w-full bg-surface border border-outline-variant/30 px-4 py-3 text-on-surface focus:outline-none focus:border-secondary transition"
						id="name"
						name="name"
						type="text"
						placeholder="山田 太郎"
						required
						autocomplete="name"
					/>
				</div>
				<div>
					<label class="block text-xs tracking-widest uppercase text-on-surface-variant mb-2" for="email" style="font-family: var(--font-label)">メールアドレス</label>
					<input
						class="w-full bg-surface border border-outline-variant/30 px-4 py-3 text-on-surface focus:outline-none focus:border-secondary transition"
						id="email"
						name="email"
						type="email"
						placeholder="you@example.com"
						required
						autocomplete="email"
					/>
				</div>
				<div>
					<label class="block text-xs tracking-widest uppercase text-on-surface-variant mb-2" for="type" style="font-family: var(--font-label)">お問い合わせ種別</label>
					<select
						class="w-full bg-surface border border-outline-variant/30 px-4 py-3 text-on-surface focus:outline-none focus:border-secondary transition appearance-none"
						id="type"
						name="type"
					>
						<option>プロジェクト相談</option>
						<option>技術的な質問</option>
						<option>その他</option>
					</select>
				</div>
				<div>
					<label class="block text-xs tracking-widest uppercase text-on-surface-variant mb-2" for="message" style="font-family: var(--font-label)">メッセージ</label>
					<textarea
						class="w-full bg-surface border border-outline-variant/30 px-4 py-3 text-on-surface focus:outline-none focus:border-secondary transition resize-none"
						id="message"
						name="message"
						rows="5"
						placeholder="ご質問やご要望をお書きください"
						required
					></textarea>
				</div>
				<button
					class="satin-gradient text-on-primary px-8 py-3 text-sm tracking-widest uppercase w-full transition hover:opacity-90"
					type="submit"
					style="font-family: var(--font-label)"
				>
					送信する
				</button>
			</form>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>
